STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
David Larry UCHYTIL, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-2070 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904
